title: The First Ever Radio Hour 12/13/21

description:
On this week’s First Ever Radio Hour, Jeremy plays tracks from Failure, Converge, Dillinger Four, Cloakroom, Gleemer, Section H8, Deadguy, Alkaline Trio, Scowl, Cave In, Greet Death, Propagandhi, and more! 
 

Subscribe to the PATREON and receive a brand new radio hour every Sunday! Thats two additional episodes a month AND you get them a day early!

Follow the show on Instagram and Twitter!
